result.name: bassetlaw-district-council-benefit-fraud
result.notes:
The Dataset shows the number of cases of irregularity and fraud that have been investigated and the monetary value identified from these investigations.

The CSV file contains data relating to the number of employees undertaking investigations, the number of cases of irregularity and fraud that have been investigated, how many cases have been prosecuted and the monetary value of these investigations and prosecutions.
result.title: Bassetlaw District Council Benefit Fraud
